sources.title: Replit vs VS Code: Features, Differences & Full Comparison
sources.snippet:
### Winner: VS Code

The open-source editor's extension ecosystem provides enormous advantage with thousands of plugins for specialized workflows. For developers working with niche languages, specialized frameworks, or complex toolchains, VS Code's extensibility is unmatched. While Replit's curated integrations work well for common use cases, VS Code adapts to virtually any development scenario through its massive extension library.
